message.distributionDefaultInviterIdTip.message: User ID of the default inviter, if the distribution link does not carry the inviter_id parameter, this user ID will be used as the default inviter.

message.distributionForceInviterIdTip.message: User ID of the forced inviter, if this ID is set, it will be used as the inviter regardless of whether the distribution link carries the inviter_id parameter.

message.originTip.message: Site domain, site configuration is bound to the domain, and the site domain cannot be changed.

message.titleTip.message: Site title, displayed in the browser tab.

message.descriptionTip.message: Site description, located in the site meta information, used for site SEO optimization.

message.logoTip.message: Site Logo, displayed at the top of the site menu when the menu bar is expanded.

message.faviconTip.message: Site Favicon, displayed in the browser tab.

message.adminsTip.message: Site admin ID, the user who first creates the site will become the admin by default, only site admins can manage the site.

message.adminsTip2.message: You can add or delete admin IDs here, you can check user IDs at https://auth.acedata.cloud

message.keywordsTip.message: Site keywords, located in the site meta information, used for site SEO optimization.

message.keywordsTip2.message: You can add or delete website keywords here, the more precise the keywords, the more beneficial for SEO optimization.

message.featuresI18n.message: Open or close multi-language support, after closing, users can only use the default language.
